    "Name": "Stinger",
    "Details": "This Mech, as you could already tell from the Name, comes from a Wealthy Family that owned a Very old Stinger. Refitting it in Current Times, This Old Design got Clantech Installed while still retaining some Inner Sphere Technology. The Weapons are Considerably upgraded, just like the Engine and as Such, this Mech is a Fearsome Scout. A Questionable IFF Package mixed with a Special Sensor make this Mech have Quasi Ewar, while not fielding a Probe or ECM. All in All, i would say this is a Good one, Boss.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Ubiquitous</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
